Gg_fy_Veranda2

Set in a small town somewhere in the country-side of Italy.  
- This is a medium sized map, and has a 32 Player spawn limit.
- There are 5 choke points in this map, each point features balanced attack & cover positions.
- No Buy Zones
- This version has been reworked and the previously long tunnel has been shorted substantially.

This version has no Buy Zones.  You can find the version with Buy Zones here:
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/108152
